[{"text": "My name is Joshua Walters.", "start": 15.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm a performer.", "start": 18.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Beatboxing)", "start": 21.26, "duration": 9.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 30.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 33.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But as far as being a performer,", "start": 37.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I'm also diagnosed", "start": 40.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "bipolar.", "start": 43.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I reframe that as a positive", "start": 50.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "because the crazier I get onstage,", "start": 52.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the more entertaining I become.", "start": 54.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "When I was 16 in San Francisco,", "start": 57.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had my breakthrough manic episode", "start": 59.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in which I thought I was Jesus Christ.", "start": 61.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Maybe you thought that was scary,", "start": 65.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "but actually there's no amount of drugs you can take", "start": 69.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that can get you as high", "start": 72.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as if you think you're Jesus Christ.", "start": 74.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 76.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I was sent to a place,", "start": 80.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "a psych ward,", "start": 83.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and in the psych ward,", "start": 85.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "everyone is doing their own one-man show.", "start": 87.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 91.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "There's no audience like this", "start": 96.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to justify their rehearsal time.", "start": 98.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "They're just practicing.", "start": 101.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "One day they'll get here.", "start": 103.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now when I got out,", "start": 107.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I was diagnosed", "start": 109.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and I was given medications", "start": 111.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "by a psychiatrist.", "start": 113.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "\"Okay, Josh, why don't we give you some --", "start": 115.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "why don't we give you some Zyprexa.", "start": 117.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Okay? Mmhmm?", "start": 120.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "At least that's what it says on my pen.\"", "start": 125.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 127.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "Some of you are in the field, I can see.", "start": 132.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "I can feel your noise.", "start": 135.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The first half of high school", "start": 139.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "was the struggle of the manic episode,", "start": 142.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and the second half", "start": 145.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "was the overmedications of these drugs,", "start": 147.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "where I was sleeping through high school.", "start": 150.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "The second half was just one big nap, pretty much, in class.", "start": 152.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "When I got out", "start": 157.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I had a choice.", "start": 159.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "I could either deny", "start": 161.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "my mental illness", "start": 164.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or embrace", "start": 166.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "my mental skillness.", "start": 170.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Bugle sound)", "start": 172.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "There's a movement going on right now", "start": 176.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to reframe mental illness as a positive --", "start": 178.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "at least the hypomanic edge part of it.", "start": 181.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now if you don't know what hypomania is,", "start": 184.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "it's like an engine that's out of control,", "start": 187.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "maybe a Ferrari engine, with no breaks.", "start": 189.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Many of the speakers here, many of you in the audience,", "start": 192.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "have that creative edge,", "start": 195.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "if you know what I'm talking about.", "start": 197.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "You're driven to do something", "start": 199.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that everyone has told you is impossible.", "start": 201.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "And there's a book -- John Gartner.", "start": 203.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "John Gartner wrote this book called \"The Hypomanic Edge\"", "start": 205.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in which Christopher Columbus and Ted Turner and Steve Jobs", "start": 208.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "and all these business minds", "start": 211.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "have this edge to compete.", "start": 213.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "A different book was written not too long ago", "start": 215.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in the mid-90s", "start": 217.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "called \"Touched With Fire\" by Kay Redfield Jamison", "start": 219.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in which it was looked at in a creative sense", "start": 222.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "in which Mozart and Beethoven and Van Gogh", "start": 225.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "all have this manic depression that they were suffering with.", "start": 228.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Some of them committed suicide.", "start": 231.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "So it wasn't all", "start": 233.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "the good side of the illness.", "start": 235.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Now recently,", "start": 238.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "there's been development in this field.", "start": 241.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And there was an article written in the New York Times,", "start": 244.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "September 2010,", "start": 247.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "that stated:", "start": 249.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "\"Just Manic Enough.\"", "start": 252.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Just be manic enough", "start": 254.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "in which investors who are looking for entrepreneurs", "start": 256.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "that have this kind of spectrum --", "start": 259.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "you know what I'm talking about --", "start": 262.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "not maybe full bipolar,", "start": 264.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "but they're in the bipolar spectrum --", "start": 267.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "where on one side,", "start": 271.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "maybe you think you're Jesus,", "start": 273.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "and on the other side", "start": 277.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "maybe they just make you a lot of money.", "start": 280.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Laughter)", "start": 282.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "Your call. Your call.", "start": 285.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "And everyone's somewhere in the middle.", "start": 288.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Everyone's somewhere in the middle.", "start": 290.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "So maybe, you know,", "start": 293.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "there's no such thing", "start": 296.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "as crazy,", "start": 298.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "and being diagnosed with a mental illness", "start": 300.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "doesn't mean you're crazy.", "start": 303.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "But maybe it just means", "start": 305.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "you're more sensitive", "start": 307.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "to what most people can't see", "start": 309.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "or feel.", "start": 311.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Maybe no one's really crazy.", "start": 313.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Everyone is just a little bit mad.", "start": 317.26, "duration": 5.0}, {"text": "How much", "start": 326.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "depends on where you fall in the spectrum.", "start": 329.26, "duration": 3.0}, {"text": "How much", "start": 333.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "depends on how lucky you are.", "start": 335.26, "duration": 4.0}, {"text": "Thank you.", "start": 339.26, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "(Applause)", "start": 341.26, "duration": 4.0}]